== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:1932_Velasco_hurricane_rainfall_totals.png|thumb]]

随着飓风逼近德克萨斯州，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家气象局]]从7月18日开始向可能受到影响的地区发布[[热带气旋警告|飓风警告]]。港口和船只不间断地收到有关风暴来袭的信息，令之后海上的渔船事故数量保持在最低水平。<ref name="District 8" />沿海地区的铁路运输在气旋来袭期间暂停，以防万一<ref name="Train Halt">{{cite news | title = No Trains Running | accessdate = 2016-12-18 | newspaper = Spokane Daily Chronicle | date = 1909-07-21 | location = New York, New York | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=halXAAAAIBAJ&sjid=9_MDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4168,2000420&dq=hurricane&hl=en | page = 1 | archive-date = 2021-11-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211111163829/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=halXAAAAIBAJ&sjid=9_MDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4168%2C2000420&dq=hurricane&hl=en }}</ref>。

登陆韦拉斯科期间，飓风对德克萨斯州沿海及部分内陆地区构成大面积破坏。虽然此前气象机构已发布警告，但风暴引发的恶劣海况依然导致多艘船只失事。大浪致使[[加尔维斯敦_(德克萨斯州)|加尔维斯敦]]附近部分船只搁浅或沉没，[[西湾_(德克萨斯州)|西湾]]（{{lang|en|West Bay}}）的“米勒号”（{{lang|en|Miller}}）井架驳船及其他多艘船只搁浅。<ref name="Texas Hurricanes">{{cite book | title = Texas Hurricane History | archivedate = 2016-12-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161201044253/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/txhur.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/txhur.pdf | format = PDF | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service | accessdate = 2016-12-18 | last1 = Roth | first1 = David M | author2 = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center }}</ref>一艘大型[[疏浚|挖泥船]]被卷进[[加尔维斯敦堤道|加尔维斯敦堤道]]，还将堤道沿线的[[电报|电报]]线缆扯断<ref name="Hurricane at Galveston">{{cite news | title = The Hurricane at Galveston | location = Galveston, Texas | page = 1 | date = 1909-07-21 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=rSMgAAAAIBAJ&sjid=VWkFAAAAIBAJ&pg=1166,3233479&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-12-18 | newspaper = The Lewiston Daily Sun | archive-date = 2021-11-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211111163839/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=rSMgAAAAIBAJ&sjid=VWkFAAAAIBAJ&pg=1166%2C3233479&dq=hurricane&hl=en }}</ref>。“米利亚姆号”（{{lang|en|Miriam}}）被木材拖沉，[[拉波特_(德克萨斯州)|拉波特]]（{{lang|en|La Porte}}）附近的“艾德·吉布斯号”（{{lang|en|Ed Gibbs}}）[[双桅纵帆船|双桅纵帆船]]断成数截。受时速估计有145公里的强风影响，“世纪号”（{{lang|en|El Siglo}}）[[蒸汽船|汽船]]被困在海上12小时之久。<ref name="Texas Hurricanes" />[[阿拉巴马州|阿拉巴马州]][[莫比尔_(阿拉巴马州)|莫比尔]]近海的船只在大浪阻挠下无法进入[[莫比尔港|海港]]<ref name="Mobile Seas">{{cite news | title = Huge Seas Off Mobile | accessdate = 2016-12-18 | newspaper = Spokane Daily Chronicle | page = 1 | location = Mobile, Alabama | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=halXAAAAIBAJ&sjid=9_MDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4168,2000420&dq=hurricane&hl=en | date = 1909-07-21 | archive-date = 2021-11-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211111163829/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=halXAAAAIBAJ&sjid=9_MDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4168%2C2000420&dq=hurricane&hl=en }}</ref>。气旋在加尔维斯敦和韦拉斯科产生三米高的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]<ref name="Metadata" />，但加尔维斯敦得到海堤的有效保护，破坏程度较轻，在海堤阻挡下潮水碰撞激起的浪花有18米高。不过，没有受到海堤影响的地区破坏程度严重，有两座[[栈桥|栈桥]]和多个[[洋亭|洋亭]]被毁。<ref name="Save Galveston">{{cite news | title = Sea Wall Saves Galveston From Wrath of Storm | newspaper = The Evening Journal | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=1t5kAAAAIBAJ&sjid=soANAAAAIBAJ&pg=1479,3566307&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-12-18 | date = 1932-07-21 | location = Galveston, Texas | page = 3 | archive-date = 2021-11-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211111163916/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=1t5kAAAAIBAJ&sjid=soANAAAAIBAJ&pg=1479%2C3566307&dq=hurricane&hl=en }}</ref>加尔维斯敦的塔彭码头坍塌，在此钓鱼的十人遇难<ref name="Seawall Save">{{cite news | title = Galveston Saved By Seawall | accessdate = 2016-12-18 | newspaper = Evening Tribune | date = 1909-07-22 | location = Galveston, Texas | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=JItcAAAAIBAJ&sjid=RVcNAAAAIBAJ&pg=3258,1942340&dq=hurricane&hl=en | page = 2 | archive-date = 2021-11-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211111163902/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=JItcAAAAIBAJ&sjid=RVcNAAAAIBAJ&pg=3258%2C1942340&dq=hurricane&hl=en }}</ref>，另外六人获“五月花号”（{{lang|en|Mayflower}}）[[游艇|游艇]]所救<ref name="Six Rescued">{{cite news | title = Six Men Are Rescued; Swept From Tarpon Pier | archivedate = 2016-08-18 | accessdate = 2016-12-18 | deadurl = no | newspaper = Dallas Morning News | date = 1909-07-22 | location = Galveston, Texas | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160818060440/http://www3.gendisasters.com/texas/10181/galveston-tx-tarpon-pier-collapse-jul-1909-six-are-rescued | url = http://www.gendisasters.com/texas/10181/galveston-tx-tarpon-pier-collapse-jul-1909-six-are-rescued }}</ref>。加尔维斯敦西部没有海堤保护，部分内陆地区被2.1米的洪水淹没<ref name="7 Feet">{{cite news | title = Seven Feet Under Water | newspaper = The Bakersfield Californian | page = 1 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=svNfAAAAIBAJ&sjid=jlQMAAAAIBAJ&pg=6088,979612&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-12-18 | date = 1909-07-21 | location = Dallas, Texas | archive-date = 2021-11-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211111160232/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=svNfAAAAIBAJ&sjid=jlQMAAAAIBAJ&pg=6088%2C979612&dq=hurricane&hl=en }}</ref>。相比之下，该市主街道的积水要浅得多，约为0.6米<ref name="Flood Streets">{{cite news | title = Hurricane Floods Galveston Streets | newspaper = Spokane Daily Chronicle | date = 1909-07-21 | page = 1 | accessdate = 2016-12-16 | location = Dallas, Texas | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=halXAAAAIBAJ&sjid=9_MDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4168,2000420&dq=hurricane&hl=en | archive-date = 2021-11-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211111163829/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=halXAAAAIBAJ&sjid=9_MDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4168%2C2000420&dq=hurricane&hl=en }}</ref>。韦拉斯科的潮水比[[1900年加尔维斯敦飓风|1900年加尔维斯敦飓风]]来袭期间还要高0.9米左右<ref name="District 8" />，该市的积水有1.2米深<ref name="Eighteen">{{cite news | title = Eighteen Lives Lost Hurricane | location = Houston, Texas | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=QrJIAAAAIBAJ&sjid=koEMAAAAIBAJ&pg=5417,2115434&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-12-18 | newspaper = Youngstown Vindicator | date = 1909-07-23 | page = 22 | archive-date = 2021-11-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211111160348/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=QrJIAAAAIBAJ&sjid=koEMAAAAIBAJ&pg=5417%2C2115434&dq=hurricane&hl=en }}</ref>。[[萨宾帕斯_(德克萨斯州)|萨宾帕斯]]（{{lang|en|Sabine Pass}}）地区被大浪淹没，同样被淹的还有[[南太平洋铁路|南太平洋铁路]]<ref name="Shutoff">{{cite news | title = Wire Communication is Shut Off From Stricken City | newspaper = Eugene Register-Guard | date = 1909-07-21 | location = Houston, Texas | page = 1 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=51tXAAAAIBAJ&sjid=WPADAAAAIBAJ&pg=5487,4133931&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-12-18 | archive-date = 2021-11-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211111160308/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=51tXAAAAIBAJ&sjid=WPADAAAAIBAJ&pg=5487%2C4133931&dq=hurricane&hl=en }}</ref>。

